title: Newly Renovated 3 Bed/3 Bath + Den/Office - Panoramic Views !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
